###### ====== PART 2: QUERYING AND FILTERING =====


### Get all tasks
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks

### Filter by status - Show only TODO tasks
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks?status=TODO

### Filter by priority - Show only HIGH priority tasks
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks?priority=HIGH

### Multiple filters - HIGH priority TODO tasks
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks?status=TODO&prority=HIGH

### Get a specific task by ID
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/1


###### ====== PART 3: TASK LISTS =================


### Create a task list for urgent items -----------
POST https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasklists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Urgent Sprint Tasks",
  "taskIds": [1, 4]
}
### -----------------------------------------------


### Create another task list for development work -
POST https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasklists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Development Work",
  "taskIds": [2, 3]
}
### -----------------------------------------------


### Get all task lists ----------------------------
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasklists
### -----------------------------------------------


### Filter task lists by name ---------------------
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasklists?name=Urgent
### -----------------------------------------------


###### ====== PART 4: UPDATING RESOURCES ==========


### Update task status from TODO to DOING ---------
PUT https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Research API best practices",
  "dueDate": "2026-01-25",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "status": "DOING"
}
### -----------------------------------------------


### Complete a task by updating status to DONE ----
PUT https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Research API best practices",
  "dueDate": "2026-01-25",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "status": "DONE"
}
### -----------------------------------------------


### Update a task list to add more tasks ----------
PUT https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasklists/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Urgent Sprint Tasks - Updated",
  "taskIds": [1, 2, 4]
}
### -----------------------------------------------


###### ====== PART 5: HTTP CACHING DEMO ===========


#### Step 1: Get a task with full response (note the Last-Modified header)
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/1
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------


### Step 2: Request again with `If-Modified-Since` header ----------------
# If not modified, returns 304 Not Modified
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/1
If-Modified-Since: Mon, 20 Jan 2026 15:30:00 GMT
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 3: Conditional update with If-Unmodified-Since ------------------
PUT https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
If-Unmodified-Since: Mon, 20 Jan 2026 15:30:00 GMT

{
  "description": "Research API best practices - COMPLETE",
  "dueDate": "2026-01-25",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "status": "DONE"
}
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------


###### ====== PART 6: CLEANUP ====================


### Delete a task
DELETE https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/3

### Delete a task list
DELETE https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasklists/1

### Verify deletion of task
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasks/3

### Verify updated task list 2 after deliting a task within it
GET https://daitodo.duckdns.org/tasklists/2
